data.description: Beautiful home located in the retirement community of Sun City.   Charm curb appeal home featuring 2 bedrooms 1 bath, drought tolerant front yard and a SPACIOUS LOT 6,969 SQFT backyard perfect for gathering with family and friends.  Enjoy fantastic HOA amenities such as a community pool, clubhouse, gym, golf course and various social activities. Conveniently, situated near shopping centers, restaurant, medical facilities, and with easy access to the 215freeway. A truly must see home!  55+ community
